Dann, Appellant, v. Gleason, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. May 27, 1889.) Action by Horace P. Dann against Samuel O. Gleason.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Ingalls, JJ.

Ho opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements.
